title: 12 essential Krautrock albums (+Krautrocksampler by Julian Cope)
description:
This is for everyone who always wanted to give krautrock a try but never really had the chance so far. In this torrent following albums have been collected:

Amon Duul II - Yeti
Can - Tago Mago
Cluster - Zuckerzeit
Faust - Faust
Grobschnitt - Solar Music Live
Guru Guru - Kanguru
Harmonia - Deluxe
Klaus Schulze - Cyborg
Kraftwerk - Kraftwerk 1
La Dusseldorf - La Dusseldorf
Neu! - Neu!
Walter Wegmuller - Tarot

Also included is the book "Krautrocksampler" by Julian Cope.
